import './Roadmap.css'; import React from 'react'; export const Roadmap = () => { return (
THE GAME PLAN
Building an inter-connected community is our number one priority. We strive for greatness and embrace risk-taking, hustling and seizing every moment.
PRE-MINT PHASE
Fortune favors the brave, and we are a community for the brave. Our goal pre-mint is to create and foster a community where people encourage one another to win and thrive. We are the pioneers of the Web3 space, the Ballers of the digital world. Our main objective is to incubate a community and give the members as much value as possible. Once our team of Ballers is formed we’ll move forward as a united front to show rest of the world what we can do.
PHASE ONE
Baller Games
To grow closer as a community and reward our holders (Ballers), we’ll be hosting fun, interactive games and giveaways. Ballers will compete in weekly tournaments for NFTs, ETH Prizes and whitelist opportunities. Our goal is to create friendships between ballers for mutual personal and financial development.
Ballers-Only Event (+2 guest)
The in-person Ballers-Only Event will be filled with giveaways and other Baller fun. This will be an opportunity to connect on a deeper level as a community and encourage greater connectivity among Ballers.
PHASE TWO
The Baller Bank
5% of our primary mint will be allocated to community funds and put in the Baller Bank. The Baller Society holders will have the influence to decide what to do with these funds.
PHASE THREE
The Baller Society Brand
Fashion isn’t just about covering up anymore. Your clothes are an extension of your personality, emotions and self. They allow you to distinguish yourself from those around you and express your identity. Ballers know just how important the fashion game is, so we want to create the most exclusive and stylish look for our holders. We aren’t talking about dropping some Gildan shirts with a ball heat-pressed on them. The ballers use fashion to exert their confidence and trademark their look. We want this brand to help bring the Baller out in all of our holders on and offline.
PHASE FOUR
The Baller-Gauntlet Airdrop
Every holder will have the chance to obtain the baller-gauntlet as a reward for maintaining your Baller NFT. The all powerful Gauntlet, made out of the same meteor that brought the ballers to life, can be used to ameliorate/transform your Baller and can also be used to redeem gifts from future partnerships.
PHASE FIVE
